q12
We get host unreachable answers after sending ARP who has requests.
This is because the ARP requests for 10.10.14.4 are not answered by PC4.

q13 
Link local address of PC1-eth0 : fe80::9a6a:5bff:fe81:c38c
 
// PC1 fe80::26fe:ceff:fe2a:9864
// PC2 fe80::3219:9fff:fe55:a871
// PC4 eth2 : fe80::eef8:50ff:feef:a360
We can see some IPv6 neighbor solicitations at first, that plays the role of ARP : it asks the MAC address of the host pinged.
Then we receive some Destination Unreachable ICMPv6 packets  from PC1

