q15
ip route
10.0.0.0/8 dev PC1-eth0  proto kernel  scope link  src 10.10.14.1 
ip -6 route
fe80::/64 dev PC1-eth0  proto kernel  metric 256 

For ipv4, all the destinations addresses in the range 10.0.0.0/8 are sent to the interface PC1-eth0
For ipv6, all the destinations addresses in the range fe80::/64 are sent to the interface PC1-eth0

q16
ip route show
10.0.0.0/8 dev PC1-eth0  proto kernel  scope link  src 10.10.14.1 
10.10.14.0/24 dev PC1-eth0  proto kernel  scope link  src 10.10.14.1 
ip -6 route show
fd24:ec43:12ca:c001:14::/80 dev PC1-eth0  proto kernel  metric 256 
fe80::/64 dev PC1-eth0  proto kernel  metric 256 

The new modifications are used for routing traffic from the host to the subnet.



